ccre.rconf

Class RConf.Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • ccre.rconf.RConf.Entry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    RConf

    public static final class RConf.Entry
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    An entry as part of the result from querying an RConfable. Could be any of the types available statically on RConf - such as F_TITLE, F_BUTTON, F_INTEGER, or others. Contains a type and a byte array of the associated data.
    Author:
    skeggsc
